**Left Sidebar Features:**
- **Collapsible Categories:** Component groups with expand/collapse
- **Active Highlighting:** Current component highlighted with accent color
- **Smooth Scroll:** Click to smooth scroll to section
- **Search Integration:** Quick filter components
- **Sticky Positioning:** Stays visible while scrolling
- **Responsive:** Drawer/hamburger menu on mobile
- **Nested Navigation:** Sub-categories with indentation
- **Icon Support:** Component icons for visual recognition

**Right Sidebar "On This Page":**
- **Auto-Generated:** Extracts h2, h3 headings from content
- **Active Section:** Highlights current section based on scroll position
- **Smooth Scroll:** Click to jump to section
- **Sticky Positioning:** Fixed position while scrolling
- **Responsive:** Hidden on mobile/tablet (< 1024px)
- **Minimal Design:** Clean, unobtrusive typography
- **Depth Indicators:** Indentation for heading hierarchy
- **Scroll Progress:** Optional progress indicator

**Main Content Area:**
- **Maximum Width:** 800-900px for optimal readability
- **Code Blocks:** Syntax highlighting with copy button
- **Live Previews:** Interactive component demos
- **Responsive Tabs:** Framework switcher (React/Vue/Next/Nuxt)
- **Dark Mode Toggle:** Per-example dark mode preview
- **Viewport Switcher:** Mobile/tablet/desktop preview sizes

**Component Documentation Structure:**
1. **Overview:** What the component does
2. **Installation:** CLI command and manual steps
3. **Usage:** Basic example with code
4. **API Reference:** Props, events, slots
5. **Examples:** Common use cases
6. **Variants:** All available variants
7. **Accessibility:** Keyboard shortcuts, ARIA
8. **Customization:** How to customize
9. **Best Practices:** When and how to use
10. **Troubleshooting:** Common issues

**Documentation Features:**
- **Live Code Playground:** Interactive component preview with real-time editing
- **Copy-Paste Code Snippets:** One-click copy for all code examples
- **Dark Mode Examples:** Toggle between light/dark previews
- **Responsive Previews:** Mobile/tablet/desktop viewport switcher
- **TypeScript IntelliSense:** Full type definitions in code examples
- **Search Functionality:** Fast, fuzzy search (Algolia or similar)
- **Version Selector:** Switch between versions
- **Framework Switcher:** Toggle between React/Vue/Next/Nuxt examples
- **Syntax Highlighting:** Beautiful code highlighting with Shiki
- **Component Preview:** Live rendering with props controls
- **Export Code:** Download component code directly

**Documentation Design Quality:**
- Premium typography (Inter, JetBrains Mono)
- Smooth page transitions
- Micro-animations on interactions
- Gradient accents and highlights
- Perfect spacing and alignment
- Responsive and mobile-optimized
- Fast loading (< 2s FCP)

