## 15. Appendices

### 15.1 Glossary
- **Component:** Reusable UI building block
- **Variant:** Different visual style of a component
- **Composition:** Combining components to create new ones
- **Headless:** Logic without styling
- **Polymorphic:** Component that can render as different elements
- **Tree-shaking:** Removing unused code from bundle

